brewery.brewery_description: Neighborhood nano-brewery on Lakeside Ave in RVA offering award winning beers brewed & poured by friendly & knowledgeable staff. Growlers & Crowlers available. Browse our homebrew store onsite, Original Gravity, as you sample 12-18 freshly crafted beers brewed right here.
